snippet.textDisplay:
I'm genuinely scared that there are people who are so willingly ignorant. I mean, common sense would allow anyone to realise that the claim is bogus:
Autism is a neurological developmental disorder.
Neurological = relating to the structure of the brain.
Developmental = happens during the brain's initial development. i.e as a foetus.
We don't have the technology to fundamentally change the structure of a person's brain without killing them.

Autism is present from birth.

Vaccines are first administered after a child has been born (duh).
The brain had already formed by then (more duh).

Therefore, it's obvious that there is no link. Logic.
